Package util

Class BSTNode<T extends Comparable<T>>

java.lang.Object
util.BSTNode<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Node
public class BSTNode<T extends Comparable<T>> extends Object implements Node
The BSTNode class represents a node in a binary search tree, storing a value of type T and references to its parent, left child, and right child.
